The paper deals with the problem of optimal power allocation in secure communications, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of information theory (cs.IT), cryptography (cs.CR), and networking (cs.NI). The use of massive MIMO relaying techniques also suggests a potential connection to signal processing (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM).
